{
  "message": "test(ansi): update insta snapshots for ANSI sequence rendering tests\n\nUpdate 11 insta snapshot files for the ANSI module test suite to reflect\ncurrent rendering output. These .snap.new files capture the expected\noutput for:\n- Foreground colors: 16-color, 256-color, truecolor, and NO_COLOR modes\n- Background colors: 16-color, 256-color, and truecolor modes\n- Text attributes (bold, italic, underline, etc.)\n- Cursor movement and positioning sequences\n- Hyperlink escape sequences\n\nThe snapshots were generated by the test suite and represent the correct\ncurrent behavior of the ANSI parser and renderer.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
